 them they have a fortune of two point two trillion dollars. The highest concentration
 of the ultrarich is in New York followed by Moscow and San Fransisco and then London
 and Los Angeles. But in total the very wealthy live in fortyseven different countries
 with Iceland Kazakstan Ukraine and Poland entering the list for the first time this year.
